        "handling": "unhandled",
        "recommendation": "Pool of 20+5 overflow serving all traffic to primary. Under load spikes, pool exhaustion will cascade into request timeouts. Add pool exhaustion metrics, queue depth monitoring, and consider separate pools for critical vs. non-critical queries."
