        "scenario": "Slow query blocking pool connections",
        "handling": "partial",
        "recommendation": "Query duration is tracked via histogram, but no statement timeout is mentioned. A single runaway query can hold a pool connection indefinitely. Set statement_timeout at the connection level (e.g., 5s for reads, 30s for writes)."
