      "reason": "Cannot assess whether the service is healthy, saturated, or degrading without connection pool utilization metrics. The 3am on-call engineer will see 500s in the error rate but have no way to determine if it is pool exhaustion, query timeouts, or primary failure without these metrics.",
      "routed_to": "Coach K"
